column1: # The readings for January, March, September and November 1952 are shown modified and bracketed, and have been omitted.
# The 1953 total has been increased by 0.06 compared to the sheet figure to match the sum of the months.
# The 1955 total has been increased by 0.01 compared to the sheet figure to match the sum of the months.
# The gauge moved about 2 miles west to the separate Anderby site in 1958.
